  @tab @code{do} @code{re} @code{mi} @code{fa} @code{sol} @code{la} @code{sib} @code{si}
@item @code{norsk}
  @tab @code{c} @code{d} @code{e} @code{f} @code{g} @code{a} @code{b} @code{h}
@item @code{português} o@*@ @code{portugues}
  @tab @code{do} @code{re} @code{mi} @code{fa} @code{sol} @code{la} @code{sib} @code{si}
@item @code{suomi}
  @tab @code{c} @code{d} @code{e} @code{f} @code{g} @code{a} @code{b} @code{h}
